<note style="-uslm-lc:I74" topic="amendments" id="id904166a6-2930-11f1-8918-be39dde81dc6"><heading class="centered smallCaps">Amendments</heading><p style="-uslm-lc:I21" class="indent0">1997—<ref href="/us/pl/105/85">Pub. L. 105–85</ref> substituted “section 3642” for “section 3655”.</p>
</note>
